{"tid":2024872,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"急! 2018 mac book pro個cursor移動方向突然調轉左","createTime":"2020-05-20T01:24:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-20T01:53:03.000Z","uid":93141,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"c84b28d6342d5ecf47a88375856e8f658a328a47","tid":2024872,"uid":93141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T01:24:49.000Z","msg":"唔係scroll個問題，而係我手指向左，cursor就向右，手指向右，cursor就向左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但上下冇調轉，試左reboot同reset nvram都冇用，可以點做好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06107e256702c7dd15fe81df21684602abeefa77","tid":2024872,"uid":93141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T01:29:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"075bdd9277e2443e5133c3ffbd3da84f626d551a","tid":2024872,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T01:35:05.000Z","msg":"搞nvram做乜<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.imore.com/how-change-trackpad-settings-your-mac\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.imore.com%2Fhow-change-trackpad-settings-your-mac&d=Vmg9VhgMmKCDk1oLDtgP7mjFlCc76q8eB7f9T8a%2Fn1E%3D&h=ae0a64b8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.imore.com/how-change-trackpad-settings-your-mac</a><br />\n<br />\nHow to change scrolling and zooming on the trackpad on a Mac<br />\n<br />\nClick the Apple icon in the upper-left corner of your screen.<br />\nSelect System Preferences... from the dropdown menu.<br />\n<br />\nOpening Preferences<br />\n<br />\nClick on Trackpad in the System Preferences window.<br />\nClick on Scroll &amp; Zoom.<br />\n<br />\nTick the box Scroll direction: Natural to have the trackpad scroll follow your finger movement."},{"pid":"c397b2186eb303fc2d84519013615d685314443c","tid":2024872,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T01:39:00.000Z","msg":"都唔得就搵天才啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41c72b2c371d7f617242641908fa837ea28054be","tid":2024872,"uid":93141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"075bdd9277e2443e5133c3ffbd3da84f626d551a","tid":2024872,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T01:35:05.000Z","msg":"搞nvram做乜<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.imore.com/how-change-trackpad-settings-your-mac\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.imore.com%2Fhow-change-trackpad-settings-your-mac&d=Vmg9VhgMmKCDk1oLDtgP7mjFlCc76q8eB7f9T8a%2Fn1E%3D&h=ae0a64b8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.imore.com/how-change-trackpad-settings-your-mac</a><br />\n<br />\nHow to change scrolling and zooming on the trackpad on a Mac<br />\n<br />\nClick the Apple icon in the upper-left corner of your screen.<br />\nSelect System Preferences... from the dropdown menu.<br />\n<br />\nOpening Preferences<br />\n<br />\nClick on Trackpad in the System Preferences window.<br />\nClick on Scroll &amp; Zoom.<br />\n<br />\nTick the box Scroll direction: Natural to have the trackpad scroll follow your finger movement."},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T01:39:23.000Z","msg":"唔係scroll阿 係cursor移動方向<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0cb0d403ac65d575280f6ace159b5eb8f8d2aa38","tid":2024872,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"41c72b2c371d7f617242641908fa837ea28054be